                <div class="kicker"><span class="kicker"><a href="https://www.dukechronicle.com/section/opinion">OPINION</a></span></div>

                <h1>Cowboy adventures in the international forum</h1>
                
                
                                    <div class="row  mt-4 mb-0 mb-md-4">
                        <div class="col-12 col-md-6">
                            <aside class="author-name">
                                    
    
                                    
            By <a href="https://www.dukechronicle.com/staff/kevin-ogorzalek-a-moment-of-your-time">Kevin Ogorzalek (A moment 
